"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349645","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2015-06-17","<p>Ambassadors and High Commissioners make decisions on the accommodation of former hon. Members in their Residences on a case-by-case basis.</p>","Aylesbury","Mr David Lidington",,"2015-06-17T14:06:56.72Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349645/answer","Biography information for Sir David Lidington","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349645/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349645/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2015-06-10","Diplomatic Service: Former Members","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, if he will publish his Department's rules and guidance governing the accommodation of former hon. Members in the official residences of UK Ambassadors and High Commissioners.","false","Biography information for Dr Andrew Murrison","South West Wiltshire","Dr Andrew Murrison","1882"
