"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349671","Department for Culture Media and Sport","false","2015-06-22","<p>Between 2009 and 2014, almost 8000 people began apprenticeships in the creative industries, plus more than 45,000 apprenticeships in ICT.</p>","Wantage","Mr Edward Vaizey",,"2015-06-22T15:46:08.917Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349671/answer","Biography information for Mr Edward Vaizey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349671/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349671/answer",,,,,"10","Culture, Media and Sport","Culture, Media and Sport","2015-06-10","Arts: Apprentices","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport, what information his Department holds on the number of apprenticeships in the cultural and creative sector.","false","Biography information for Chris Bryant","Rhondda","Chris Bryant","2004"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349672","Prime Minister","false","2015-06-16","<p>Ministers who are not members of an Implementation Taskforce can attend on an ad hoc basis by invitation of the Chair.</p>","Witney","Mr David Cameron",,"2015-06-16T15:59:51.677Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349672/answer","Biography information for Mr David Cameron","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349672/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/349672/answer",,,,,"23","Prime Minister","Prime Minister","2015-06-10","Task Forces: Young People","1","House of Commons","To ask the Prime Minister, if he will appoint a Minister in the Department for Culture, Media and Sport to the Earn or Learn Implementation Taskforce.","false","Biography information for Chris Bryant","Rhondda","Chris Bryant","2005"
